      • newTransaction

        public static void newTransaction(Bus bus,
                                  BusStop busStop)
        Creates transaction involving given bus and bus stop. Passengers that are traveling to the given bus stop are removed and new passengers are placed in the bus. It happens at the moment of creation of transaction. Transaction length is computed at the basis of number of passengers being unloaded and loaded.
        Parameters:
        bus - bus being taking part in transaction
        busStop - bus stop taking part in transaction
